Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.19,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.51,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.05,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.65,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.17,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.40,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是怎样的暴风雨来临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.35,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.25,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你…
