Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.19,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.23,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.77,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.27,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.46,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.12,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.29,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.86,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.61,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.06,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.57,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.77,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…维多利卡 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:37.87,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.37,ZW,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进去
